125
00:07:23,060 --> 00:07:24,180
Is this your Qiulubai?

126
00:07:24,500 --> 00:07:26,700
[Qiulubai]

127
00:07:31,540 --> 00:07:32,580
Since everyone's here,

128
00:07:33,020 --> 00:07:34,140
