129
00:07:36,060 --> 00:07:36,660
Mr. Xun.

130
00:07:37,460 --> 00:07:38,220
Miss Yueya.

131
00:07:39,660 --> 00:07:40,500
Also, Little Master.

132
00:07:55,940 --> 00:07:57,940
So the third taster is Ruofeng.

133
00:08:06,500 --> 00:08:07,900
Let's start with Qiulubai.

134
