since I've had this.

136
00:08:13,140 --> 00:08:14,260
I miss it dearly.

137
00:08:21,220 --> 00:08:22,340
So this is Qiulubai?

138
00:08:29,420 --> 00:08:30,300
As expected of Qiulubai.

139
00:08:30,540 --> 00:08:31,060
Yes.

140
00:08:34,620 --> 00:08:35,820
The smell alone is intoxicating.

141
00:08:36,500 --> 00:08:37,220
I've never smelled

142
00:08:37,220 --> 00:08:37,860
anything this good.

143
00:08:37,860 --> 00:08:39,060
So, this is
the most famous liquor Qiulubai

144
00:08:39,500 --> 00:08:40,940
in Tianqi.

145
00:08:41,780 --> 00:08:42,860
It truly lives up to its name.

146
00:08:49,300 --> 00:08:50,340
You have a whole jar of liquor

147
