162
00:09:17,900 --> 00:09:18,420
Such a pity.

163
00:09:28,100 --> 00:09:29,380
You're here for the challenge.

164
00:09:29,580 --> 00:09:30,740
Don't show others that you're eager
to drink your rival's liquor.

165
00:09:31,700 --> 00:09:32,180
Well, it's not contradictory.

166
00:09:37,900 --> 00:09:39,780
This batch is even richer

167
00:09:41,820 --> 00:09:42,580
than the last Qiulubai I tasted.

168
00:09:58,340 --> 00:10:01,100
Xie, you have certainly honed
your brewing skills

169
00:10:01,180 --> 00:10:02,460
