181
00:10:54,700 --> 00:10:56,740
The warmth of spring,

182
00:10:56,980 --> 00:10:59,020
the passion of summer,

183
00:10:59,140 --> 00:11:01,260
and the melancholy of autumn.

184
00:11:02,340 --> 00:11:03,100
