190
00:11:25,220 --> 00:11:26,860
That's too much exaggeration,
young man.

191
00:11:27,260 --> 00:11:28,540
Serve your liquor.

192
00:11:29,860 --> 00:11:30,380
All right.

193
00:11:45,100 --> 00:11:45,660
Luoxia,

194
00:11:46,860 --> 00:11:47,740
