218
00:13:06,620 --> 00:13:08,420
I'm quite eager to try.

219
00:13:10,620 --> 00:13:11,100
Please, go ahead.

220
00:13:12,020 --> 00:13:12,660
Mister,

221
00:13:13,620 --> 00:13:14,100
