225
00:14:03,460 --> 00:14:03,980
Wonderful!

226
00:14:05,980 --> 00:14:07,060
What marvelous liquor!

227
00:14:13,220 --> 00:14:13,860
How good is it?

228
00:14:15,740 --> 00:14:18,500
It feels like

229
00:14:19,380 --> 00:14:20,940
I've returned to my youth

230
00:14:22,300 --> 00:14:23,700
which was full of romantic dreams.

231
00:14:23,940 --> 00:14:25,380
Before those romantic settings,

232
00:14:25,780 --> 00:14:27,140
I was filled with confidence

233
00:14:27,340 --> 00:14:28,660
and determination to achieve my goals.

234
00:14:32,260 --> 00:14:33,260
