245
00:16:17,980 --> 00:16:19,180
Why is

246
00:16:19,220 --> 00:16:20,220
Ruofeng's head steaming?

247
00:16:20,340 --> 00:16:21,340
That's not steam.

248
00:16:21,460 --> 00:16:22,180
It's zhenqi.

249
00:16:23,380 --> 00:16:24,100
Zhenqi?

250
00:16:24,540 --> 00:16:25,780
