253
00:16:27,940 --> 00:16:28,580
and

254
00:16:28,620 --> 00:16:30,340
we can only feel it

255
00:16:30,340 --> 00:16:31,140
when it's flowing in our bodies.

256
00:16:31,900 --> 00:16:33,700
I've never heard

257
00:16:33,740 --> 00:16:35,700
of it being visible to the naked eye.

258
00:16:35,940 --> 00:16:37,140
When all sanmei zhenqi are perfected,

259
00:16:37,580 --> 00:16:38,900
